- Yeah.

6
00:00:28,029 --> 00:00:29,780
- Yeah. Yeah, there's something wrong.
- Yeah.

7
00:00:29,823 --> 00:00:32,909
- Hi.
- Hi.

8
00:00:32,993 --> 00:00:35,537
- Oh, my God. It's beautiful! Oh, wow!
- Mm-hmm.

9
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:36,538
One bathroom...

10
00:00:36,621 --> 00:00:39,249
- There's one bathroom downstairs.
- Okay. It's gorgeous.

11
00:00:39,332 --> 00:00:42,669
- [Charlie] One bathroom downstairs.
- Oh, love the ceiling. Pocket doors.

12
00:00:43,587 --> 00:00:47,716
- There is a second bathroom. [chuckles]
- [chuckling] Okay!

13
00:00:48,633 --> 00:00:50,760
There is a third bathroom off the primary!

14
00:00:50,844 --> 00:00:54,347
- That's great! Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! [squeals]
- Yes! Yay! Yeah! Yes! Yes!

15
00:00:54,431 --> 00:00:55,514
- [chuckles] Aw.
- Oh, my God.

16
00:00:55,557 --> 00:00:57,266
Just tell us what's wrong with it, Diane.
Please.

17
00:00:57,309 --> 00:01:00,145
- Yeah.
- Absolutely nothing. It is perfect.

18
00:01:00,228 --> 00:01:02,022
We are legally obligated to tell you

19
00:01:02,105 --> 00:01:06,401
that last year there was a triple homicide
on site, but, I mean, the school district.

20
00:01:06,484 --> 00:01:07,569
- Sold.
- We'll take it.

21
00:01:07,652 --> 00:01:11,114
- Great. I am so happy for you two.
- [laughs]

22
00:01:11,197 --> 00:01:13,199
Just don't Google the O'Connells.

23
00:01:13,783 --> 00:01:14,683
Oh.

24
00:01:15,410 --> 00:01:17,078
["Good Friend" playing]

25
00:01:30,425 --> 00:01:32,886
Yo, Omar,
I need you to sterilize tank two.

26
00:01:32,969 --> 00:01:34,512
Oh, that's not gonna happen, big boy.

27
00:01:34,596 --> 00:01:36,473
Hilarious. Go sterilize tank two.

28
00:01:36,556 --> 00:01:39,392
No. 'Cause I'm the brewmaster now, fool.

29
00:01:40,602 --> 00:01:41,603
The fuck you just say?

30
00:01:41,686 --> 00:01:45,190
I said, "No,
'cause I'm the brewmaster now, fool."

31
00:01:46,274 --> 00:01:48,026
