- Yeah, kinda.
- Yes, dude.

39
00:02:03,458 --> 00:02:08,671
It is not gonna work, okay?
You have no idea how much shit I can eat.

40
00:02:10,966 --> 00:02:14,553
Okay, let's do this. You want me to, uh,
unload the truck, uh, then, or...

41
00:02:14,636 --> 00:02:15,929
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

42
00:02:16,012 --> 00:02:17,264
