that I would love to ask.

44
00:02:19,307 --> 00:02:21,350
Oh, you're gonna interview me?
Perfect. Let's do this.

45
00:02:21,393 --> 00:02:24,813
- Um, why do you want this position?
- I don't.

46
00:02:25,939 --> 00:02:29,442
Here's one. How do you brewmaster?

47
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:33,446
First thing the wedding planner
asks me is,

48
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:34,656
