52
00:02:41,830 --> 00:02:43,873
- Oh. She was wonderful.
- Oh.

53
00:02:43,957 --> 00:02:46,751
Very chill. Yeah.
Let me get you her website.

54
00:02:47,627 --> 00:02:49,107
- Oh, God. She's dead.
- [smacks lips]

55
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:53,174
- Wow, "Natural causes."
- Oh, very chill. Like, literally chill.

56
00:02:53,675 --> 00:02:57,220
- God, we're so old. Ugh, depressing.
- Jesus.

57
00:02:57,304 --> 00:02:59,184
Why don't you start
with just a Pinterest board?

58
00:02:59,264 --> 00:03:02,642
- You know, with all your ideas.
- Oh, my God. That sounds so boring.

59
00:03:02,726 --> 00:03:03,935
