So, just don't say it ever again.

66
00:03:18,909 --> 00:03:21,453
- Sure. Sure. [chuckles]
- [chuckling]

67
00:03:21,536 --> 00:03:24,456
Are you inviting Will to the housewarming?

68
00:03:24,539 --> 00:03:28,293
Uh, we're inviting our new neighbors
and Charlie's work friends.

69
00:03:28,376 --> 00:03:32,422
And it's people from different worlds and,
you know, when Will and I get together,

70
00:03:32,505 --> 00:03:35,133
we just, like, get carried away
and act like idiots.

71
00:03:35,884 --> 00:03:37,802
- Back to your new house.
- Mm-hmm.

72
00:03:37,886 --> 00:03:40,764
