75
00:03:45,977 --> 00:03:47,437
[chuckles]

76
00:03:48,021 --> 00:03:50,941
- How many people died here?
- I don't know. Like, three or four.

77
00:03:51,024 --> 00:03:52,817
[guests chattering]

78
00:03:57,614 --> 00:04:01,409
So, I got two wedding theme ideas,
but I think we can bring 'em together.

79
00:04:01,493 --> 00:04:03,245
I'm not planning your wedding, so…

80
00:04:03,328 --> 00:04:05,245
Relax. I didn't say you
were gonna plan my wedding.

81
00:04:05,288 --> 00:04:06,728
