- Good? Yeah.

98
00:04:43,118 --> 00:04:45,077
Look. You know, we're two blocks
from Gemma's house.

99
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,289
So we don't have to give rides
to Frances anymore.

100
00:04:47,372 --> 00:04:50,709
- They can just hang out all the time.
- And do whatever that is they're doing.

101
00:04:50,792 --> 00:04:51,793
